There are 3 types of actions - Active, Defensive, Responsive:
 Active involves math heavy problems of check dam construction ,etc. to get ahead of the threat. 
 Defensive actions involve resource allocation problems of sending the right amount of boats to correct places based on weather data, 
 Responsive actions involve political decisions of prioritizing which people for evacuation, handling of Rohingya migrants, etc. \


